## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="47576-184">Il valore predefinito è Ssl3 &#124; Tls &#124; Tls11 &#124; Tls12.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47576-184">The default value is Ssl3 &#124; Tls &#124; Tls11 &#124; Tls12.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="47576-185">Versioni di framework precedenti alla 4.6 supportano solo Tls e Ssl3.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47576-185">Versions of the framework prior to 4.6 only support Ssl3 and Tls.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="47576-186">Se questi non sono inclusi, la comunicazione con le versioni precedenti del framework non sarà possibile.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47576-186">If these are not included, communication with earlier versions of the framework will not be possible.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="47576-187">Specificando Tls11 e/o Tls12 disabiliterà l'utilizzo del protocollo Ssl3, anche se è stato incluso.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47576-187">Specifying Tls11 and/or Tls12 will disable the usage of Ssl3, even if it has been included.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```  
NetTcpBinding netTcpBinding = new NetTcpBinding(SecurityMode.Transport);  
netTcpBinding.Security.Transport.ClientCredentialType = TcpClientCredentialType.Certificate;  
CustomBinding b = new CustomBinding(netTcpBinding);  
SslStreamSecurityBindingElement sslStream = b.Elements.Find<SslStreamSecurityBindingElement>();  
sslStream.SslProtocols = SslProtocols.Tls11 | SslProtocols.Tls12;  
EndpointAddress a = new EndpointAddress("net.tcp://contoso.com/TcpAddress");  
ChannelFactory<ICalculator> cf = new ChannelFactory<ICalculator>(b, a);  
cf.Credentials.ClientCertificate.SetCertificate(  
    StoreLocation.LocalMachine,  
    StoreName.My,  
    X509FindType.FindByThumbprint,  
    "0000000000000000000000000000000000000000");  
```
